abstract:

Speaker:: Efe Öge Track: PyCon: Web Why do some .pdf files open in a browser at a lick? At the same time, others wait for the answer of where to download? I know that some pages load as fast as lightning. Besides, There are examples which just poodle along. In this presentation, The reasons and solutions will come up. Recorded at the PyConDE & PyData Berlin 2022 conference, April 11-13 2022. https://2022.pycon.de More details at the conference page: https://2022.pycon.de/program/SVZEXS Twitter: https://twitter.com/pydataberlin Twitter: https://twitter.com/pyconde
